definitions.definition: A locality and former civil parish in Norton, Cuckney, Holbeck and Welbeck parish, Bassetlaw district, Nottinghamshire , England ( OS grid ref SK5674 ) .
A community in West Grey township, Grey County , Ontario , Canada .
